---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Thank You | Pakenham Fencing"
  description="Thanks for your fencing enquiry. Pakenham Fencing will be in touch soon with your Colorbond, timber, pool or rural fencing quote."
  canonical="https://pakenhamfencingco.com.au/thanks/">
  <Fragment slot="head"><meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow"></Fragment>
  <section class="hero hero-suburb">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Message received</span>
      <h1>Thanks &mdash; we&rsquo;ll be in touch.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Your fencing enquiry has come through to Pakenham Fencing. We&rsquo;ll review
        the details and get back to you shortly with the next step toward your quote.
        Need us sooner? Call <a href="tel:+61390030108">(03) 9003 0108</a>.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/">Back to home</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>While you wait.</h2>
      <div style="max-width: 60rem;">
        <p>
          Have a look at the kind of fencing we build across the Cardinia growth
          corridor &mdash; it might help you picture the finished job before we
          speak. Explore
          <a href="/services/colorbond-fencing/">Colorbond fencing</a>,
          <a href="/services/timber-paling-fencing/">timber paling fencing</a>,
          <a href="/services/pool-safety-fencing/">pool safety fencing</a> to
          AS 1926.1,
          <a href="/services/rural-acreage-fencing/">rural &amp; acreage fencing</a>
          and <a href="/services/gates-automation/">gates &amp; automation</a> &mdash;
          or see fencing in your area such as
          <a href="/cardinia-lakes/">Cardinia Lakes</a>,
          <a href="/officer/">Officer</a> and
          <a href="/beaconsfield/">Beaconsfield</a>, plus the wider
          <a href="/cardinia-shire/">Cardinia Shire</a> hub.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
